      "content": "hey, quick question. i just got some antibiotics for this skin infection i had. i've been taking them for 3 days now and the redness and swelling are like, totally gone. honestly i feel 100% better already. do i really need to keep taking them for the full 10 days if the infection isn't even showing anymore? i'm just worried about putting too many chemicals in my body if i don't need them anymore.",
